Ample guestrooms, beginning at 40m2, were completely renovated in 2010 to highest luxury standard and feature elegantly furnished balconies with garden or pool views. 

Guests will also enjoy an indoor heated pool, whirlpool, sauna, Turkish baths and massage service.

Rio Verde Restaurant offers a superb breakfast buffet with show cooking, as well as varied lunch and dinner buffets. In summer, La Hiedra restaurant serves Mediterranean treats outdoors, and the patio bar offers live entertainment and cocktails.

The residential area of Puerto Banus offers many shopping and dining options, and the best golf options on the Costa de Sol are nearby (within 20 km). 

Shuttle from airport or high-speed train.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The Melia Marbella Banus is located in the heart of Puerto Banus, one of the most exclusive areas in Marbella. It is only 45 minutes from Malaga's international airport and only 7 minutes from Puerto Banus. With Marbella and its charming old quarter just 6 km away, the hotel's magnificent location is ideal for day trips to Andalusia's spectacular cities: Granada, Seville and Cordoba, or its picturesque towns such as Ronda, Mijas and Gibraltar.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>STANDARD - GUEST_ROOM - Spacious rooms, recently renovated and fully equipped with a wide range of comforts, decorated in soothing tones in a very contemporary style. The large private terraces open on to the Swimming pools and beautiful gardens. Notable for their very large size, measuring approximately 40 m2, they provide two Queen-size beds and have been designed to satisfy the needs of guests, with new 32inch Plasma TV, marble floors and attractive crafted wooden furnishings. A perfect combination of comfort, technology and elegance throughout the hotel.

